                </div>
            </div>

            <button class="modal-btn"
                style="background: #1A73E8; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px;"
                onclick="retryCamera()">Start Identity Scan</button>
            <p style="font-size: 11px; color: #9aa0a6; margin-top: 15px;">Your data is encrypted and protected by Paynet
